HEADWORD: Tarweed
<hw>Tar"weed`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A
name given to several resinous-glandular composite plants of California,
esp. to the species of <gen>Grindelia</gen>, <gen>Hemizonia</gen>, and
<gen>Madia</gen>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

